text: Star Channel (Arabic: ) was an Middle Eastern pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as the Middle Eastern version of Discovery Home & Health on 8 May 2009 and started broadcasting in 16:9 aspect ratio on 22 November 2011. On 9 July 2024, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that the Middle Eastern version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as Star Channel on 6 August 2024. However, on 6 March 2025, it was later announced that the channel would cease broadcasting on 6 April 2025. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|8 May 2009-6 August 2024 file:Star Channel 2023.svg|6 August 2024-6 April 2025 Category:Television channels in Asia
